<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Krilen, are you saying that for every elemental of roughly the same level as a warder, that the elemental should be better than the warder in some important way, but that the warder pet can be better in some other way? Yes?<br>
<br>
