<br>
   Hell maybe vi could implement some kind of double attack that only occurs when we do not have the pet up. From what I have read it is pretty much agreed up on that beast pets need upgrading, how much though is the problem. If we did get double attack that would negate the need for a really good pet and we would get our dps upgrade without stepping on mages toes. I do not really know, other than double attack any other way to raise our dps without the pet being raised enough to bother mages. Or vi could add in something totally unique which I doubt vi will do no doubt due to extra coding they do not want to do.<br>
