<br>
This is for lvl 60:<br>
1) We need a DPS upgrade.<br>
2) To get this upgrade we either raise pet DPS or lord DPS<br>
3) Current lord DPS is less than mage/necro DPS in short AND long term fights. PLUS we need to be within melee range to do dmg while we are *Very* poor tanks. The worst tank among all hybrids/melees. Our defensive skills are capped LOW, we are a leather class, our hp isn't *that* high (lower than SK, etc).<br>
4) If your pet is to be better than ours, then our lord DPS has to be better than your mage DPS (nuking). Not for short term fights (of course) but definitely for middle/long fights. In fact, to maintain balance (not counting your epic *or* our 50% slow since they are both hard-hard-hard to get) your mage damage + mage-pet DPS has to be very close to lord + warder DPS. On *average* (over short/middle/long fights).  Can you all agree to this?<br>
5) If *our* pet is to have higher DPS than yours (I am *NOT* advocating this, just listing it as one of the POSSIBLE solutions to the DPS upgrade) then our lord DPS can be BELOW mage (nuking) DPS.<br>
<br>
Thats my view of the current situation and possible solution paths. I would prefer #4. In all likelihood they will implement a *combination* of #4 and #5. Upgrade our pets BELOW mage pets but ABOVE necromancer pets (I mean, COMMON, beastlords are *SO* much more dependent on pets than necromancers). Then they can upgrade our lord DPS to move us into balance with mages/etc. This is what I expect them to do.<br>
<br>
Now to attempt to defuse some counter-arguments:<br>
1) Argument: BST shouldn't do so much DPS, they have so much utility!<br>
Answer: As a hybrid, SK/Paladin are DEFENSIVE and BST/RNG are OFFENSIVE. Let us look at utility though: Druids/wizards can port, druids can sow/heal/dot/DD/evac, magicians can summon/mod-rod/DS/gate (heh)/etc, necromancers I won't even get STARTED on, etc. I think BST do *not* fall into the top 3 utility classes on everquest, not even close.<br>
<br>
2) Argument: BST can tank so much better than mages, so your class DPS shouldn't be as high!<br>
Answer: Your right =). We should be below the mage class in DPS. How much lower is the question that needs answering. We are the worst non-caster tanks in the game. Heck, clerics/Shamans can likely tank almost as well as we can..ESPECIALLY with their huge heals. (We have really low CAPs on our defensive skills...) Because of all this I think our DPS shouldn't be far below mage DPS...Shrug...My opinion.<br>
<br>
Those are the two relevant arguments I came up with, different arguments apply when considering balance vs other classes (ie: Monks, etc).<br>
<br>
Anyhow, I hope this post was clear and that it won't illicit any flames as I tried to be most reasonable and to RESPECT your concerns as mages. Good day my fellow pet owners =).<br>
<br>
-Drexion <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=363.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=363.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=363.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showMessageRange?topicID=363.topic&start=81&stop=99>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showPrevMessage?topicID=363.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showNextMessage?topicID=363.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=363.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.threadControl?topicID=363.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=363.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=363.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=f